SUMMARY:NewFest: ROD PARKER PRODUCTION
DESCRIPTION:When Death Crashes a Dinner Party \n\n\n\nNewFest: Rod Parker Production\n\n\n\nDirected by Joe Antoun\n\n\n\n\nAt a refined cocktail hour meant to honor the mysteriously absent Edmund Ford\, five guests exchange martinis\, pleasantries\, and—very quickly—accusations. What begins as polite chatter devolves into a chaotic unraveling of secrets\, grudges\, and unexpected reckonings with one another and themselves. \n\n\n\n\n\n\n\nDates\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\nEvent Info\n\n\n\nVenue\n\n\n\n\n\nDetails\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n1 Hour 15 Mins \n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\nAge 13+ \n\n\n\n\n\nHealth & Safety Information
URL:https://emersontheatres.org/event/newfest-rod-parker-production/
LOCATION:Greene Theatre\, 10 Boylston Place 6th floor\, Boston\, Massachusetts\, 02116\, United States
ATTACH;FMTTYPE=image/png:https://emersontheatres.org/wp-content/uploads/sites/81/2025/09/networksThumb.png
END:VEVENT
